Professional bodies are set up to govern standards in a set area and lead research and development of that area. 

 

3 digital bodies to know for your exams: 

  British computing society (BCS) 
  
  Institution of  analysts & programmers (IAP) 
  
  Association for computer machinery (ACM) 

 

BCS code of conduct, main points: 

  Make IT for everyone 
  
  Show what you know, learn what you don't  
  
  Respect the organization or individual you work for 
  
  Keep IT real. Keep IT professional. Pass IT on.  
